    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Documents that announce the birth of a child. Often these include the parents' names, and sometimes physical details of the child. This term may be extended to printed cards, newspaper listings, electronic mailings, or other historical forms.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
